## Appendix A: Daily Security Checklist

### Opening
- [ ] Inspect exterior for signs of overnight break-in or vandalism
- [ ] Verify all vehicles are accounted for and undisturbed
- [ ] Check that camera system is recording
- [ ] Confirm alarm system disarmed properly; check for alerts
- [ ] Count opening register float and document

### Closing
- [ ] All customer vehicles secured in lot or inside
- [ ] All keys returned to locked key cabinet; verify against work orders
- [ ] Register reconciled; excess cash dropped to safe
- [ ] All bay doors closed and locked
- [ ] All entry doors locked and secured
- [ ] Camera system and alarm system armed
- [ ] Walk exterior perimeter before leaving

